    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep luster without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin smells like new, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine example for the most discerning collector or driver.",
