    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all weekend warriors and project lovers! This car is the perfect canvas for someone looking to take on a full restoration or seeking a budget-friendly source for parts. While it currently requires substantial mechanical and cosmetic work to be roadworthy again, it offers a fantastic opportunity for a hands-on owner to bring it back to life at a great entry-level price!",
